name: Staked ACME
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.
The smart-contract owner can mint new tokens, please proceed with caution.

description.en:
stACME is an ERC-20 token, issued by Accumulated Finance and representing the staked ACME on the Accumulate protocol.
Accumulated Finance is a liquid staking and DeFi platform for the Accumulate protocol and ACME/WACME token.
Native ACME staked in liquid staking are held in accumulated.acme multi-signature staking account.
stACME tokens staked on Accumulated Finance will earn the Accumulate protocol’s staking APR.
Additionally it's possible to provide stACME liquidity into stACME/WACME Curve pool to earn additional rewards.
